General.Name: Hartshead Resources NL
General.Description: Hartshead Resources NL engages in the oil and gas exploration and development activities in the United Kingdom, Gabon, and Madagascar. It primarily holds a 100% interest in the License P2607 comprising of five blocks covering 729.5 square kilometers located in the Southern North Sea of the United Kingdom. Hartshead Resources NL is headquartered in Perth, Australia.
